name: Bonkers
description: Bonkers go bonkers for thumpin' on stumpies! Uh, we mean stumps. The understated sapling that the Bonkers thump their fuzzy heads against is no Great Tree, but hey - theyll take what they can get! It still emanates a particular magic that compels Bonkers to beat up on bark. While certainly befuddling to us, this behavior is only natural to the other inhabitants of the Bonkers percussive home dimension.
breedingTime: Breeding Time: 9 hr, Enhanced Time: 6 hr 45 min
